data.description: One word to describe this beautiful home is NEW! This well-maintained home will seem like it has yet to be lived in, located in Loumos Heights Subdivision. Open concept kitchen with everything from quartz countertops, gorgeous cabinetry, crown molding, oversized island, and stainless steel appliances. The main suite has double sinks on a luxurious vanity and a large walk-in closet. Over a half-acre backyard has a large concrete patio to entertain. The 2-car attached garage has ample parking and an extra concrete slab.  The tall ceilings, plumbed basement, and egress window await your ideas to be an incredible space with tons more square footage, within 10 Minutes from I-94 and a short distance to Illinois and Milwaukee. Set up your private showing ASAP!
